metadata.name: 100 NFTS 1/1
metadata.description:
On Monday 10/10, the angel number that signifies new beginnings, Iman Europe sold out of her "Surrender" collection. 100 NFTs were sold in 5 minutes! 

This was a remarkable moment in Web3 that the entire community celebrated.To make sure we never forget it, I've decided to frame and mint the tweet so it can live forever on the blockchain.

100 NFTs sold in the middle of a bear market! I'll cheers to that!

To more Web3 wins. Salud.

[winner of this auction will receive a physical copy of this tweet in a similar gold frame.]
